# 支付系统

V2BoardPro支持多种支付方式，包括支付宝、微信支付、加密货币支付等。

## 支付模型

- [app/Models/Payment.php](mdc:app/Models/Payment.php) - 支付方式配置
- [app/Models/Order.php](mdc:app/Models/Order.php) - 订单数据

## 支付处理器

支付处理器位于 [app/Payments/](mdc:app/Payments/) 目录下，包括：
- [app/Payments/AlipayF2F.php](mdc:app/Payments/AlipayF2F.php) - 支付宝当面付
- [app/Payments/WechatPayNative.php](mdc:app/Payments/WechatPayNative.php) - 微信支付
- [app/Payments/StripeCredit.php](mdc:app/Payments/StripeCredit.php) - Stripe信用卡支付
- [app/Payments/CoinPayments.php](mdc:app/Payments/CoinPayments.php) - 加密货币支付

## 支付控制器

- 支付相关控制器: [app/Http/Controllers/V1/Guest/PaymentController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/V1/Guest/PaymentController.php)
- 订单控制器: [app/Http/Controllers/V1/User/OrderController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/V1/User/OrderController.php)

## 支付服务

支付业务逻辑封装在 [app/Services/PaymentService.php](mdc:app/Services/PaymentService.php)
订单业务逻辑封装在 [app/Services/OrderService.php](mdc:app/Services/OrderService.php)

## 订单处理

订单处理作业: [app/Jobs/OrderHandleJob.php](mdc:app/Jobs/OrderHandleJob.php)
